      <gmd:abstract><gco:CharacterString>The MDBC Mapping, Groundtruthing and Modeling team along with USM will conduct AUV acquisition at  multiple deepwater dome sites for 11 operational days using the RV Point Sur.  The mission will   focus on two objectives - 1) Collect high-resolution multibeam bathymetry and backscatter over   Macondo wellhead and impact area (MC252) using the USM Eagle Ray (ER) AUV, 2) collect high resolution   data at other proximal dome features where significant feature anomalies of been identified from existing  data.</gco:CharacterString></gmd:abstract>
      <gmd:purpose><gco:CharacterString>Testing </gco:CharacterString></gmd:purpose>
      <gmd:supplementalInformation><gco:CharacterString>UxS operational layer: Dataset or product; outcome: completed</gco:CharacterString></gmd:supplementalInformation>
